OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy
OL,6,Fovernight with band of rain moving
OL,7,Finto the north during the evening,
OL,8,Falthough this becoming more sporadic
OL,9,Fand patchy as it moves southeastwards
OL,10,Fovernight. Feeling cooler than of late
OL,11,Fwith light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FLargely fine and cloudy Sunday
OL,14,Fwith some bright or sunny spells at
OL,15,Ftimes, these more frequent into the
OL,16,Fevening. Feeling a lot cooler than of
OL,17,Frecent in brisk northeasterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
